    <comment>Supersedes sr#1362303: bugzilla-mcp 0.15.1 rename now builds against %{primary_python} instead of a hardwired python313 flavour (identical RPM today; Obsoletes/Provides python313-bugzilla-mcp kept literal). Paired with delete request sr#1362304 for python-bugzilla-mcp.</comment>
