    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>Update bugzilla-mcp to 0.16.0: add attachment support (list_attachments + download_attachment with auto/inline/save modes and private opt-in), new --download-dir option / BUGZILLA_DOWNLOAD_DIR env var writing to an owner-only 0700 dir, and improved Bugzilla REST API error reporting. No dependency changes (pyproject identical bar the version). Builds clean (noarch, 0 rpmlint badness); source_validator green.</comment>
